Date: Sat 11 Jan 2003
From: Pablo Nart <p.nart@virgin.net>
Source: La Prensa (Panama), Sat 11 Jan 2003, (in Spanish) [Translated
summary by Mod.JW]
<http://www.prensa.com/hoy/mundo/843963.html>

El Salvador and Honduras: dengue hemorrhagic fever case reports
---------------------------------------------------------------
EL SALVADOR: Health authorities confirm that an 11 year old girl died of
dengue hemorrhagic fever (DHF) in hospital on Sat 4 Jan 2003.
HONDURAS: Health authorities have so far registered at least 3 suspected
cases of DHF, awaiting confirmation.
